  <brief_title>A Qualitative Study Into How Patients Deal With Chemotherapy-related Side Effects at Home</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Qualitative Study Into How Patients With Cancer Deal With Chemotherapy-Related Side Effects at Home</official_title>
